<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hi TKP Administrator!</h1>
  <p>An order has just been placed with The Kitten Project.</p>
  <p>The details of the order are as follows:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Customer n°<%= @user.id %></li>
    <li>Customer email: <%= @user.email %></li>
    <li>Amount paid: <%= number_to_currency(@order.amount, unit: "€", separator: ",", delimiter: "", format: "%n %u") %></li>
    <li>Items ordered:
      <ul>
        <% @order.cart.cart_items.each do |cart_item| %>
          <li><%= cart_item.item.title %> -- <%= number_to_currency(cart_item.item.price, unit: "€", separator: ",", delimiter: "", format: "%n %u") %> -- x <%= cart_item.quantity %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>